Package jade.content.onto.basic

Class Summary
Action This class implements the action operator of the FIPA SL0 action.
Done This class implements the done operator of the FIPA SL0 action.
Equals This class implements the = operator of the FIPA SL0 action.
FalseProposition This class represents the FALSE proposition i.e. a predicate that is always false.
Result This class implements the result operator of the FIPA SL0 action.
TrueProposition This class represents the TRUE proposition i.e. a predicate that is always true.
